    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start, but I need to get a bit more granular for the training manual. Specifically on the \"neat hair\" part—what kind of hairstyles or grooming habits would you recommend to ensure someone looks truly polished and doesn't look \"unkept\" or \"distracting\" in a high-stakes environment?",
